review.practice_name: Smilekraft Dental Clinic, NFC, New Delhi

survey_response.review_text: For quite sometime I had been experiencing pain in my jaws on opening my mouth alongwith a clicking sound. This had gradually worsened over time till I decided to see someone for it. I went to 2-3 doctors before I finally met Dr. Ruchir Mishra first at his South Ex clinic and then later at this new clinic. His understanding of such conditions is superb and he is extremely patient with his patients. He also believes in very conservative treatment methods to start with rather than advising expensive tests and procedures straight away. His stepwise approach in solving my problem and the continuous encouragement through the difficult 5-6 months went a very long way in finally giving me the much awaited relief. I then went onto take more treatment from his wife Dr. Sony who was also very good. Today, as I complete my treatment with Dr. Ruchir , I only have very good things to say about him for helping me recover from a very depressing phase on my life and I recommend him and his team to all those who look forward to evidence based methodical treatment at very reasonable prices. God bless Doc!

Kindness in the world today is rare. Kindness from strangers almost unheard of. You do not know me on a personal level and yet you have gone out of your way to show me kindness, generosity and sincere care. I want you to know that you have touched my heart. I appreciate your kindness so much. **** *** **** * ******* *** *** My overall health and self-image had been severely undermined by the condition of my teeth and mouth.  You have given me a renewed sense of hope and restored my physical and mental health with their compassion and concern. As for your kindness, I hope in my everyday life to try and pass it on to others. I thank you for my teeth, my smile, and your care. It is privilege and a pleasure to know you. Thank you all and God bless you.

review_reply.reply_text: Thanks so much for your feedback. I am happy to note that you are happy with the dental implants we did for you. The crowns have also gone off well and we are happy to have lived upto your expectations.

survey_response.review_text: I had got 2 implants placed earlier in US. Now when I needed 3 more to be fixed, I decided to get it done on my trip to India. Must say I was overwhelmed by the professionalism, compassion *** ******** ****** of Dr. Mishra and his team. Not money minded at all and maintaining highest standards of sterilization and great treatment planning, they completed the process to my satisfaction. Now I am getting the crowns placed and some additional work for my front teeth done with his wife Dr. Sony. God Bless the team!

A great overall experience. Had first visited Dr. Ruchir for an issue related to my wisdom tooth which had been troubling me. He first did a gum treatment there which kept things fine for more than a year. But when the problem recurred, he removed it for me very painlessly and I felt comfortable during the procedure as well as after it. Thereafter I also got a missing molar replaced by him with a dental implant and a cap. Everything has gone very well for me and I am very satisfied with both his approach to his patients as well as his treatment planning and performance of the procedures. Would happily recommend him and his team including Dr. Sony and others.

Hidden in South Ex Part 1Just behind the Market in the still residential part of south Ext. is this Gem 💎 of a Dental clinic, with very caring, patient friendly, and very positive set of Doctors Dr. Ruchir Mishra and all. Correct and precise treatment, a very patient and detailed explanation  of actual problem in your teeth, and a "patient first" professionalism  to be inspired by. In this Dental patient's heaven one can be assured best treatment at most appropriate cost. Unlike the money driven clinics, here one can be assured No hidden charges, X-rays or additional not required procedures are ever pushed on patient. It is such a refreshingly positive experience whenever I visit them for my dental issues. I highly recommend Smilecraft South Ex Part1 and Dr. Mishra to everyone looking for best dental treatment.

Dr Ruchir Mishra .. Excellent Doctor !!! 
.So glad that I met him as he never failed to explain the details of each step of the treatment ,ensuring that I fully understand well and is confident of the treatment undertaken .
Though i was  initially scared of the Periapical Surgery that I had to go through , his words of comfort ,his skills and knowledge to the finest detail and his clear explaination made me confident .. I knew that I was in safe hands ! Would definitely recommend to visit him as he is one of the finest doctors . Never had such experience here in my hometown in Imphal , Manipur nor in other parts of Delhi !

I had one missing tooth on either side in my lower jaw and needed replacement for it. I had found out about Dr. Sony through the internet when searching for a nice Cosmetic Dentist in Delhi for my smile correction. While visiting her I also discussed my missing tooth problem with Dr. Ruchir who told me all the possibilities. After much thought I decided to go ahead with dental implants and Dr. Ruchir did a very smooth and painless job. His treatment planning is elaborate but such doctors who are very methodical always make patients feel reassured and give us a lot of peace of mind. I am very happy to recommend him.

contexts.text: Teeth Replacement with Implants in three days

survey_response.review_text: I was visiting India from St. Petersburg in Russia for some work. I also needed some dental treatment and was searching for the ***t dentist in Delhi to do the treatment. I was also wanting a dental clinic with reasonable charges. After much online search I found Dr. Ruchir and their clinic in South Delhi. I got 3 implants placed for my lower front teeth. They also fixed temporary crowns. All the work was finished in just 3 days. I have now come back again after 4 months and got permanent caps for my teeth. I am very happy with everything. They are recommended.

It has been a truly satisfying experience getting my treatment down by Dr. Ruchir Mishra and his team. I had a difficult wisdom tooth removal to be done which he did with great ease. He spent extra time making me comfortable and with his expertise, saved on cutting my bone too. He has also placed 2 implants for my other missing teeth. The procedure went very smoothly and I find their charges quite reasonable too. They have taken really good care of me and my mother and made us feel so much at home. God Bless Dr. Mishra and the Smilekraft team.

While on my visits to Delhi to see his wife Dr. Sony, I also got my left upper wisdom tooth removed by Dr. Ruchir. I was delaying it since long because of the stories of discomfort that I had heard of because of this procedure. I must say Dr. Ruchir was very gentle and methodical in his approach and I was very comfortable during the procedure and even after it. I have now also got an implant fixed for one of my other missing tooth. The best thing I liked about their clinic is the way they precisely plan everything down to the T and take great pains to explain everything to the patient and finally let us make our decisions instead of trying to force anything on us.

I was very impressed with the way he helped me throughout my RCT and two extractions. He guided me on how should i be careful not skipping my other medicines. Extractions were painless. Gave me all the proper information on RCT. You can trust him blindly, makes all process painless and pleasant experience.

I have suffered for many years with dental problems. Now I came to Dr. Mishra and got 3 very badly decayed teeth removed and then replaced with 2 implants. He will now give me a bridge and I am very happy with all the treatment done till now. Very professional and well-mannered polite team.

I had a badly paining lower wisdom tooth for a very long time. I was scared to get it removed because it was badlky stuck in the bone. Finally, with Dr. Ruchir's reassurance and counselling I gathered the courage. The procedure went off very smoothly. I have had good experiences at this clinic and have now become regular to this place because I liked their services and they treat their patient so well. Great efforts. All the best!!

I had an amazing experience with Dr. Ruchir. He took the proper time to understand my situation and assessed it carefully before recommending anything. He explained the solution well and patiently. I am extremely satisfied with the treatment and the safety precautions that were followed.

Visiting Dr Ruchir for treatment, it's always reassuring to feel you are under very trusted and highly abled hands. He does exactly that and the conduct of the entire treatment process is highly professional.

The doctor was very friendly and very informative. review_reply.reply_text: Thank you so much for taking out time to write such an elaborate feedback for us. We are happy we were able to take care of your dental treatment needs nicely and the results left you happy and satisfied.

survey_response.review_text: I had problems in 3 of my teeth. While one was saved and capped by Dr. Sony, the other 2 needed to be removed. Dr Ruchir did the extractions very smoothly and comfortably for me and then planned the replacements with dental implants and graft. I was quite comfortable and happy with the way the procedures were carried out and the results are very satisfying. These doctors are very good and very caring too.

I have got my missing teeth replaced here by Dr. Ruchir Mishra. I had heard and read a lot of good things about him on the internet. Also, my brother had seen him earlier and recommended him strongly. They gave me all the different treatment choices and I opted for dental implants after Dr. Mishra's guidance. He has done both stages of the procedure very nicely for me and I have now got caps fixed. It has been a great experience and well worth it.

I am very happy with the entire treatment process and methodology followed at this clinic by Dr. Mishra. They give all the patients a lot of time and individual attention and ensure the best results always. I came in a lot of pain and with poor condition of my gums and a badly decayed wisdom tooth. The procedures they undertook gave me a lot of relief and now I am completely pain-free. Highly recommend Dr. Mishra and team for all dental problems.

I had earlier got treatment here by Dr Sony for gap closing and crooked teeth. I had visited now for an upper chewing tooth that had a bad decay and was quite painful. Dr. Ruchir did a difficult removal for my tooth with a lot of ease and later placed an implant in the missing area. My tooth is now replaced and I am happy to be able to eat again from there. Procedures were quite painless and the doctors here re very nice and friendly. Great experience for me.

I have got my missing teeth replaced here using dental implants. And I must say I am very satisfied with the entire procedure. First of all, the entire explanation of the procedure and all the pros and cons are very nicely done. Dr. Ruchir also gave options of different implant systems he uses. The way he does the procedure is quite painless and I have now got new caps fixed on the implants. Very happy with everything.

I am very happy with the Consultation and treatment provided by Dr. Ruchir and his team. I had many missing teeth and his suggestions and line of treatment has really helped me. Charges are also very reasonable and transparent and they give us patients all the possible treatment choices. Very satisfied.

Doctor Ruchir is so nice and i really did not feel a single discomfort while my surgery. We all know how sensitive is our tooth and gums but at smilecraft i was so well taken care its beyond your thaughts....thank you very much. Recomend this to every individual

I had a lot of pain during jaw movements. I had seen two people earlier and they had both suggested removing the lower wisdom tooth. One doctor also suggested a lot of elaborate stuff to treat my joint and the treatment estimate was very expensive. Then I found out about Dr Ruchir and came to see him. He listened to me patiently and examined me properly. He suggested removing an upper wisdom tooth and some simple follow up things. He explained the reasons for his suggestions in detail. I was a little apprehensive since he was the first one to suggest removal for the upper one. But I must say all his plans turned out correct. Within 2 days of the removal, I started feeling relief and after a week he started me on some exercise and a splint. It has been almost 2 weeks now and I am almost 95% relieved of my pain and jaw movement problems now. Very thankful to Dr. Ruchir and his wife Dr Sony for their care as also their precise treatment plans *** ***** *******

You know that you are in good hands when your doctor is willing to listen to you and discuss every minor detail in length concerning your health issue. Both Dr Ruchir Mishra and Dr Soni Mishra have an eye for detail and will go to great lengths to provide you with details of everything from the treatment to the precautions and even your multivitamins until you are completely satisfied. Not to mention the flexibility in accommodating your schedule for the treatment. 
I can’t recommend them both enough. 
Thank you for your help!

It was enlightening that Dr Ruchir did not recommend apicoectomy in my case, and his surgical knowledge really stood forth as he explained that there's a crucial nerve that loops back in the lower jaw, and if not done carefully or as last resort, apicoectomy can result in issues later on without even removing the infection completely. **** ****** ****** ** ********** *** ********* and the respect he even accords to a patient's intelligence in needing the understand their own biology. He tries and simplifies the biology as well as the treatment to a great extent and was always very kind, patient, and relaxed during treatment. Especially when my jaw would lock due to TMJ during the treatment, he would calmly slide it back into the socket much to my shock and relief! :D Dr Ruchir really is an excellent oral surgeon and I'm glad I went to smilekraft!

survey_response.review_text: I had 2 missing teeth. For them, I got dental implants placed here. I came back again to India after 5-6 months and then have got caps placed on them. I am now very happy with the result. There charges are much lesser and they are very genuine. Dr. Ruchir gives you all the options and takes very good care of the patient. I have also got aligners made for my daughter for the correction of her gaps between the teeth and their crooked appearance. She is now wearing them back in Canada and the treatment is proceeding as planned and explained to us. The whole experience was very smooth and seamless. What I like most about them is how methodical they are. Kudos to them.

This was our first visit. Dr Ruchir Mishra gave time to the patient - checked all previous records and prescriptions and then clearly explained the cause behind the problem that, in his experience, patient was facing. Both Dr Ruchir Mishra and his partner doctor Dr Sony Mishra were patient, polite and respectful and heard us out at length.  We are now looking forward to seeing what treatment roadmap they will propose for the patient (keeping in mind patient limitations and reservations) and hoping to see results from the treatment in 4-6 months. This first visit was an overall good experience.

I have been visiting them for more than 9 years now. Earlier, we used to come to them all the way from Uttarakhand after my son introduced us to them. Both me and my husband have always been very satisfied with all the treatment done till now. I have got implants and crowns done and have had no trouble till now. In between, since travelling was a issue, I have seen some other dentists as well. But I have never got as much satisfaction and comfort anywhere else.. **** *** **** ******* *** ************** More importantly, they are very polite and always make you feel at home. God Bless them.

I am very happy with the care they take and their very good knowledge.

I have a lot of dental problems related to my teeth and gums but was always very scared of any dental treatment because of a mortal fear of injections. But I must say Dr. Mishra and his team have been simply brilliant in allaying all my fears and making me completely comfortable through all my treatment. The results are excellent and my teeth are much healthier now.

You guys are great guys I have ever seen so far. I have had a very pleasant experience with my treatment at your clinic. Cheers to you and your Smilekraft team.
